data.description: Situated on a large, flat, corner lot in Riverside, this 2 bedroom brick ranch is ready for new owners! Enjoy the quiet sitting porch on the front of the home, before you cozy up next to the brick fireplace inside. One bedroom and bathroom on main with main-floor laundry and large eat-in kitchen/dining space. Downstairs, there are two dens, a family room with egress and closet, and a bedroom with egress and closet. A double car garage and shed are on the property for all of your storage needs. The yard is fenced already for you. Closing contingent on seller finding suitable housing.
